chunks.lyrics: This is my first tab, it's A Horse Called Golgotha by Baroness.
I tabbed it for the people who asked for a tab after watching
my cover of the song which can be found here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YQoJOKQKX2E
I just used some live videos and my own ears to figure it out so
The tuning is DGCFAD which surprised me since Baroness songs are
usually in Drop A#. Some of the songs on Blue Record are in Drop C
like Jake Leg and The Gnashing.
